Our special features:

1) Beatufully colered buttons, with active background!
If playes presses an illeagle button, button will be red untill he releases.
Otherwise, butten will turn green.

2)
Player can cancel last button selected, by pressing on the button with
the right-click.

3)
The amazing refresh button!
If player finds no more words and has time left over, he can try his luck
with a new board!
all socre and words guessed are kept.

4)
Well designed text box!
Player cannot manually add words to text box. and if words reach end of text box,
player can scroll through text box to see all of his words.


